File Organizer and Email Extractor
This project contains two Python programs:

1. A file organizer that moves all .jpg images from one folder to another
2. An email extractor that finds and saves email addresses from a text file

FEATURES
File Organizer:
* Scans a source folder
* Moves all .jpg files to a destination folder
* Automatically creates destination folder if it does not exist

Email Extractor:
* Reads data from a text file
* Extracts all email addresses using regular expressions
* Saves extracted emails into a new file

TECHNOLOGIES USED
* Python 3
* os module (file handling)
* shutil module (file moving)
* re module (regular expressions)

HOW IT WORKS

Part 1: File Organizer

* Checks for destination folder
* Creates it if not present
* Moves all .jpg files from source_images to jpg_files

Part 2: Email Extractor

* Reads content from data.txt
* Uses regex pattern to find email addresses
* Saves results into emails.txt

OUTPUT
* .jpg files moved to:
  jpg_files/

* Extracted emails saved in:
  emails.txt
